  <entry>
    <title>Archlinux安装教程</title>
    <link href="/2022/03/13/Archlinux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <url>/2022/03/13/Archlinux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Archlinux安装教程"><a href="#Archlinux安装教程" class="headerlink" title="Archlinux安装教程"></a>Archlinux安装教程</h1><h2 id="大体流程"><a href="#大体流程" class="headerlink" title="大体流程"></a>大体流程</h2><ul><li>1.镜像下载以及光盘刻录,并启动光盘</li><li>2.同步时间</li><li>3.磁盘分区以及挂载以及格式化文件系统</li><li>4.安装系统</li><li>5.生成fstab文件</li><li>6.chroot到新的系统</li><li>7.设置时间,区域,语言,并同步时间</li><li>8.设置hostname,以及hosts文件</li><li>9.安装系统引导,并生成引导文件</li><li>10.完成安装<h3 id="1-下载镜像以及光盘刻录"><a href="#1-下载镜像以及光盘刻录" class="headerlink" title="1.下载镜像以及光盘刻录"></a>1.下载镜像以及光盘刻录</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#获取镜像</span><br>wget https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinux/iso/2022.03.01/archlinux-2022.03.01-x86_64.iso<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#刻录镜像</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=/archlinux.iso of=/dev/sda<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-同步时间"><a href="#2-同步时间" class="headerlink" title="2.同步时间"></a>2.同步时间</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#启动时间服务</span><br>timedatectl set-ntp <span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#同步时间</span><br>hwclock --systohc<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-磁盘分区以及挂载"><a href="#3-磁盘分区以及挂载" class="headerlink" title="3.磁盘分区以及挂载"></a>3.磁盘分区以及挂载</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#磁盘分区</span><br>cfdisk /dev/sda<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#创建文件系统</span><br>mkfs.vfat /dev/sda1<br>mkswap /dev/sda2<br>mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda3<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#挂载文件系统</span><br>mount /dev/sda3 /mnt<br><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> /mnt/boot<br>mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/boot<br>swapon /dev/sda2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-安装系统"><a href="#4-安装系统" class="headerlink" title="4.安装系统"></a>4.安装系统</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pacstrap /mnt base linux linux-firmware<br><span class="hljs-comment">#base 为基础系统</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#linux 为linux内核</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#linux-firmware为驱动程序包</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-生成fstab文件"><a href="#5-生成fstab文件" class="headerlink" title="5.生成fstab文件"></a>5.生成fstab文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">genfstab /mnt &gt;&gt; /mnt/etc/fstab<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-chroot到新环境"><a href="#6-chroot到新环境" class="headerlink" title="6.chroot到新环境"></a>6.chroot到新环境</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">arch-chroot /mnt<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-设置时间区域以及语言"><a href="#7-设置时间区域以及语言" class="headerlink" title="7.设置时间区域以及语言"></a>7.设置时间区域以及语言</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime<br><br>vim /etc/locale.gen<br>去掉一下两行<br>en_US.UTF-8 UTF-8<br>zh_CN.UTF-8 UTF-8<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;LANG=&quot;</span>en_US.UTF-8<span class="hljs-string">&quot; &gt; /etc/locale.conf</span><br><span class="hljs-string">locale-gen</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="8-设置hostname-hosts文件"><a href="#8-设置hostname-hosts文件" class="headerlink" title="8.设置hostname,hosts文件"></a>8.设置hostname,hosts文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;Arch&quot;</span> &gt;&gt; /etc/hostname<br>vim /etc/hosts<br>127.0.0.1 localhost<br>::1     localhost<br>127.0.1.1 localhost.localdomain<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="9-安装系统引导"><a href="#9-安装系统引导" class="headerlink" title="9.安装系统引导"></a>9.安装系统引导</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">pacman -S grub<br>grub-install --target=x86_64-efi --efi-directory=/boot<br>grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="10-完成安装"><a href="#10-完成安装" class="headerlink" title="10.完成安装"></a>10.完成安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#设置root用户密码</span><br>passwd root<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#退出系统</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">exit</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#卸载磁盘</span><br>umount /mnt/boot<br>umount /mnt<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#重启系统</span><br>reboot<br><span class="hljs-comment">#取出安装介质</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul>]]></content>
    
    
    <categories>
      
      <category>linux发行版基本使用</category>
      
    </categories>
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>linux发行版安装</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
