  <entry>
    <title>gentoo linux安装教程(systemd)</title>
    <link href="/2022/03/09/gentoo-linux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/"/>
    <url>/2022/03/09/gentoo-linux%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="gentoo-linux安装教程-systemd"><a href="#gentoo-linux安装教程-systemd" class="headerlink" title="gentoo linux安装教程(systemd)"></a>gentoo linux安装教程(systemd)</h1><h2 id="1-环境准备"><a href="#1-环境准备" class="headerlink" title="1.环境准备"></a>1.环境准备</h2><blockquote><h3 id="1-1-文件准备"><a href="#1-1-文件准备" class="headerlink" title="1.1.文件准备"></a>1.1.文件准备<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/17a2f9de4d2040e686deffa38529e5fb.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_d3F5LXplbmhlaQ,shadow_50,text_Q1NETiBAdGhlZnJhZ21lbnRlZA==,size_19,color_FFFFFF,t_70,g_se,x_16#pic_center"></h3><p>可以使用openrc管理服务也可以使用systemd,(这里使用systemd)</p></blockquote><h3 id="1-2-光盘刻录"><a href="#1-2-光盘刻录" class="headerlink" title="1.2.光盘刻录"></a>1.2.光盘刻录</h3><p>1.windows可使用rufus刻录installiation到U盘<br>2.linux可使用dd刻录</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">dd</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>=./install-amd64-minimal-20220102T170545Z.iso of=/dev/sda<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3-启动刻录好的U盘"><a href="#1-3-启动刻录好的U盘" class="headerlink" title="1.3.启动刻录好的U盘"></a>1.3.启动刻录好的U盘</h3><h2 id="2-磁盘分区与挂载"><a href="#2-磁盘分区与挂载" class="headerlink" title="2.磁盘分区与挂载"></a>2.磁盘分区与挂载</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#磁盘分区</span><br>fdisk /dev/sda<br><span class="hljs-comment">#磁盘格式化</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#boot分区</span><br>mkfs.vfat /dev/sda1<br><span class="hljs-comment">#swap分区(如果内存足够可以不使用swap)</span><br>mkswap /dev/sda2<br><span class="hljs-comment">#根分区</span><br>mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda3<br><span class="hljs-comment">#分区挂载</span><br>mount /dev/sda2 /mnt/gentoo<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-获取stage3并将其解压"><a href="#3-获取stage3并将其解压" class="headerlink" title="3.获取stage3并将其解压"></a>3.获取stage3并将其解压</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">wget https://bouncer.gentoo.org/fetch/root/all/releases/amd64/autobuilds/20220109T170538Z/stage3-amd64-systemd-20220109T170538Z.tar.xz<br>tar -Jxf stage3-amd64-systemd-20220109T170538Z.tar.xz -C /mnt/gentoo<br><span class="hljs-comment">#将之前格式化的boot磁盘挂载</span><br>mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/gentoo/boot<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-portage配置以及软件仓库配置"><a href="#4-portage配置以及软件仓库配置" class="headerlink" title="4.portage配置以及软件仓库配置"></a>4.portage配置以及软件仓库配置</h2><h3 id="1-修改portage配置文件"><a href="#1-修改portage配置文件" class="headerlink" title="1.修改portage配置文件"></a>1.修改portage配置文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">nano /mnt/gentoo/etc/portage/make.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># These settings were set by the catalyst build script that automatically</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># built this stage.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Please consult /usr/share/portage/config/make.conf.example for a more</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># detailed example.</span><br>COMMON_FLAGS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;-march=native -O3 -pipe -fstack-protector-strong&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#设置编译参数(-march-native可以根据cpu指令集进行优化,-O3优化级别)</span><br>CFLAGS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;COMMON_FLAGS&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#C编译参数</span><br>CXXFLAGS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;COMMON_FLAGS&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#C++编译参数</span><br>FCFLAGS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;COMMON_FLAGS&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>FFLAGS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;COMMON_FLAGS&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br>ACCEPT_KEYWORDS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;amd64&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#可接受的软件包等级(稳定与不稳定)(这里为全局keyworkds,若想为特定软件包指定特定的Keyworkds(可以在/etc/protage/portage.accpet_keywords</span><br>ACCEPT_LICENSE=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;*&quot;</span><br>MAKEOPTS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;-j8 -l7.2&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#根据cpu核心数来配置(一般配置为cpu核心数+1)</span><br>CHOST=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;x86_64-pc-linux-gnu&quot;</span><br>EMERGE_DEFAULT_OPTS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;--jobs=8 --load-average=7.2 --ask --quiet-build --keep-going --with-bdeps=y&quot;</span><br>GRUB_PLATFORMS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;efi-64&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#配置GRUB架构平台</span><br>L10N=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;en-US en&quot;</span><br>LINGUAS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;en-US en&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#镜像源</span><br>NETEASE=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://mirrors.163.com/gentoo/&quot;</span><br>NEUSOFT=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://mirrors.neusoft.edu.cn/gentoo/&quot;</span><br>TSINGHUA=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/gentoo/&quot;</span><br>CDS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;http://mirrors.yun-idc.com/gentoo/&quot;</span><br>ALI=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://mirrors.aliyun.com/gentoo/&quot;</span><br>BIT=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://mirror.bit.edu.cn/gentoo/&quot;</span><br>USTC=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/gentoo/&quot;</span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#设置语言</span><br>AUTO_CLEAN=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;yes&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#设置自动清理</span><br>VIDEO_CARDS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;intel i965 iris nvidia&quot;</span><br>INPUT_DEVICES=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;libinput&quot;</span><br>MICROCODE_SIGNATURES=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;-S&quot;</span><br>LC_MESSAGES=C<br><br><br>PORTDIR=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/var/db/repos/gentoo&quot;</span><br>DISTDIR=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/var/cache/distfiles&quot;</span><br>PKGDIR=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/var/cache/binpkgs&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#设置软件包缓存目录</span><br>PORTAGE_TMPDIR=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;/tmp&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#设置portage构建软件包目录(如果内存较大,建议设置在内存里面)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># This sets the language of build output to English.</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># Please keep this setting intact when reporting bugs.</span><br>LC_MESSAGES=C<br>GENTOO_MIRRORS=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;USTC&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#设置GENTOO镜像源</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><h3 id="2-配置Gentoo软件仓库"><a href="#2-配置Gentoo软件仓库" class="headerlink" title="2.配置Gentoo软件仓库"></a>2.配置Gentoo软件仓库</h3></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> --parents /mnt/gentoo/etc/portage/repos.conf<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> /mnt/gentoo/usr/share/portage/config/repos.conf /mnt/gentoo/etc/portage/repos.conf/gentoo.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-修改软件仓库配置文件"><a href="#3-修改软件仓库配置文件" class="headerlink" title="3.修改软件仓库配置文件"></a>3.修改软件仓库配置文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">将软件源uri替换成国内的(以下为中科大)<br>sync-uri = rsync://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/gentoo-portage<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="5-配置基本系统环境"><a href="#5-配置基本系统环境" class="headerlink" title="5.配置基本系统环境"></a>5.配置基本系统环境</h2><h3 id="1-复制dns配置文件"><a href="#1-复制dns配置文件" class="headerlink" title="1.复制dns配置文件"></a>1.复制dns配置文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> --dereference /etc/resolv.conf /mnt/gentoo/etc/resolv.conf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-挂载必要的文件系统"><a href="#2-挂载必要的文件系统" class="headerlink" title="2.挂载必要的文件系统"></a>2.挂载必要的文件系统</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">mount --types proc /proc /mnt/gentoo/proc<br>mount --rbind /sys /mnt/gentoo/sys<br>mount --make-rslave /mnt/gentoo/sys<br>mount --rbind /dev /mnt/gentoo/dev<br>mount --make-rslave /mnt/gentoo/dev<br><span class="hljs-comment">#假如用的不是gentoo的livecd,需要加入以下两句</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">test</span> -L /dev/shm &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> /dev/shm &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> /dev/shm<br>mount --types tmpfs --options nosuid,nodev,noexec shm /dev/shm<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> 1777 /dev/shm<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="6-进入新的系统环境"><a href="#6-进入新的系统环境" class="headerlink" title="6.进入新的系统环境"></a>6.进入新的系统环境</h2><h3 id="1-进入到新环境的shell-并载入基本环境变量"><a href="#1-进入到新环境的shell-并载入基本环境变量" class="headerlink" title="1.进入到新环境的shell,并载入基本环境变量"></a>1.进入到新环境的shell,并载入基本环境变量</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">chroot</span> /mnt/gentoo /bin/bash<br><span class="hljs-built_in">source</span> /etc/profile<br><span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PS1=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;(chroot)<span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;PS1&#125;</span>&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-挂载boot分区"><a href="#2-挂载boot分区" class="headerlink" title="2.挂载boot分区"></a>2.挂载boot分区</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">mount /dev/sda1 /boot<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-安装cpuid2cpuflags"><a href="#3-安装cpuid2cpuflags" class="headerlink" title="3.安装cpuid2cpuflags"></a>3.安装cpuid2cpuflags</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">emerge --ask app-portage/cpuid2cpuflags<br><span class="hljs-comment">#cpuid2cpuflags</span><br>将输出的值加入make.conf文件并作为CPU_FLAGX_X86=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;&quot;</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-安装ccache加快编译速度"><a href="#4-安装ccache加快编译速度" class="headerlink" title="4.安装ccache加快编译速度"></a>4.安装ccache加快编译速度</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">emerge --ask ccache <br><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> -p /var/cache/ccache<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chown</span> root:portage /var/cache/ccache -R<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> 2775 /var/cache/ccache -R<br><span class="hljs-comment">#之后去掉/mnt/gentoo/etc/portage/make.conf中关于“ccache”的注释</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-安装aria2加快emerge的下载速度"><a href="#5-安装aria2加快emerge的下载速度" class="headerlink" title="5.安装aria2加快emerge的下载速度"></a>5.安装aria2加快emerge的下载速度</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">emerge --ask aria2<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-设置时区-systemd"><a href="#6-设置时区-systemd" class="headerlink" title="6.设置时区(systemd)"></a>6.设置时区(systemd)</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">ln</span> -snf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime<br>emerge --config sys-libs/timezone-data<br>hwclock --systohc<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-设置区域"><a href="#7-设置区域" class="headerlink" title="7.设置区域"></a>7.设置区域</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">nano /etc/locale.gen<br><span class="hljs-comment">#去掉一下两行注释</span><br>zh_CN.UTF-8 UTF-8<br>en_US.UTF-8 UTF-8<br><br>locale-gen<br>eselect locale list   <span class="hljs-comment">#查看可用系统时区和地区配置</span><br>eselect locale <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> X    <span class="hljs-comment">#设置区域</span><br>env-update &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">source</span> /etc/profile &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">export</span> PS1=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;(chroot) <span class="hljs-variable">$&#123;PS1&#125;</span>&quot;</span><span class="hljs-comment">#重新加载环境</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="8-更新并构建系统"><a href="#8-更新并构建系统" class="headerlink" title="8.更新并构建系统"></a>8.更新并构建系统</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><br>eselect profile list<br><span class="hljs-comment">#(列出可选的配置文件)</span><br>eselect profile <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> ?<br><span class="hljs-comment">#(设置系统的配置文件)</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#同步ebuild数据库</span><br>emerge-webrsync<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#更新系统</span><br>emerge --ask --verbose --update --deep --newuse @world<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="8-编译内核"><a href="#8-编译内核" class="headerlink" title="8.编译内核"></a>8.编译内核</h2><h3 id="1-编译内核"><a href="#1-编译内核" class="headerlink" title="1.编译内核"></a>1.编译内核</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#获取内核源码</span><br>emerge --ask sys-kernel/gentoo-sources<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#收集硬件信息</span><br>emerge --ask sys-apps/pciutils<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> /usr/src/linux<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#配置编译选项</span><br>make menuconfig<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#编译内核</span><br>make -j8<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#安装内核以及内核模块</span><br>make install &amp;&amp; make modules_install<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-生成initramfs-可选"><a href="#2-生成initramfs-可选" class="headerlink" title="2.生成initramfs(可选)"></a>2.生成initramfs(可选)</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#(当/usr /var等重要分区与根分区分离时需要initramfs进行挂载)</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#安装genkernel工具</span><br>emerge --ask sys-kernel/genkernel<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#生成initramfs</span><br>genkernel --install initramfs<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-引导以及驱动配置"><a href="#3-引导以及驱动配置" class="headerlink" title="3.引导以及驱动配置"></a>3.引导以及驱动配置</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">emerge --ask sys-kernel/linux-firmware<span class="hljs-comment">#这个软件包包含了常用的</span><br>驱动程序<br>emerge --ask sys-firmware/intel-microcode<span class="hljs-comment">#intel 微码文件</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-生成fstab文件"><a href="#4-生成fstab文件" class="headerlink" title="4.生成fstab文件"></a>4.生成fstab文件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#如果使用的archlinux的livecd,可以使用archlinux的genfstab自动生成fstab文件</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#genfstab /mnt/gentoo &gt; /mnt/gentoo/etc/fstab</span><br>blkid &gt;&gt; /etc/fstab<br>修改/etc/fstab文件<br>UUID=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;203C-2BDD&quot;</span>        /boot   vfat    defaults 0 1<br>UUID=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;5afdfbc9-0c66-4a13-8f29-da00199af5de&quot;</span> /   ext4 defaults defaults,noatime,discard 0 2<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-配置系统引导"><a href="#5-配置系统引导" class="headerlink" title="5.配置系统引导"></a>5.配置系统引导</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment">#安装grub2</span><br>emerge --ask --verbose sys-boot/grub:2<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#安装bootloader</span><br>grub-install --target=x86_64-efi --efi-directory=/boot --bootloader-id=Gentoo<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">#生成grub配置文件</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> /boot/grub<br>grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-其他配置"><a href="#6-其他配置" class="headerlink" title="6.其他配置"></a>6.其他配置</h3><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><code class="bash">#设置主机名nano /etc/hostname#设置root用户密码passwd root#安装一些基本的网络管理软件包emerge --ask net-wireless/iw net-wireless/wpa_supplicant net-misc/networkmanager net-misc/dhcp net-misc/dnsmasq#如果是当服务器可以设置静态ip地址nano /etc/systemd/network/10-wired-dhcp.network(数字代表优先级(越小越优先)#静态网络配置[Match]Name=eth0[Network]Address=192.168.50.100/24DNS=192.168.50.1DNS=114.114.114.114[Route]Gateway=192.168.50.1Metric=100#设置网络服务开机自启动ln -snf /run/systemd/resolve/resolv.conf /etc/resolv.confsystemctl enable systemd-resolved.servicesystemctl enable systemd-networkd.service</code></pre></div>]]></content>
    
    
